programme.title: Tien jaar Terug: 2014-2015
programme.desc: In Tien jaar Terug duiken we in het Eredivisieverleden. In het seizoen 2014-2015 gaan Ajax en Frank de Boer op jacht naar de vijfde landstitel op rij. Om dit te verhinderen trekt PSV de buidel. Luuk de Jong komt voor 5,5 miljoen euro over van Borussia Mönchengladbach. Bij de nummer twee van het vorige seizoen, Feyenoord, vindt een leegloop plaats. Hoe vergaat het de nieuwe trainer Fred Rutten in Rotterdam-Zuid? FC Dordrecht keert na twintig jaar weer terug op het hoogste niveau. Lukt het de ploeg van Ernie Brandts om voor de tweede keer in de clubgeschiedenis niet als laatste te eindigen.

programme.title: Tien jaar Terug
programme.desc: In Tien jaar Terug duiken we in het Eredivisieverleden. In het seizoen 2014-2015 gaan Ajax en Frank de Boer op jacht naar de vijfde landstitel op rij. Om dit te verhinderen trekt PSV de buidel. Luuk de Jong komt voor 5,5 miljoen euro over van Borussia Mönchengladbach. Bij de nummer twee van het vorige seizoen, Feyenoord, vindt een leegloop plaats. Hoe vergaat het de nieuwe trainer Fred Rutten in Rotterdam-Zuid? FC Dordrecht keert na twintig jaar weer terug op het hoogste niveau. Lukt het de ploeg van Ernie Brandts om voor de tweede keer in de clubgeschiedenis niet als laatste te eindigen.

programme.title: Tien jaar Terug
programme.desc: In Tien jaar Terug duiken we in het Eredivisieverleden. In het seizoen 2014-2015 gaan Ajax en Frank de Boer op jacht naar de vijfde landstitel op rij. Om dit te verhinderen trekt PSV de buidel. Luuk de Jong komt voor 5,5 miljoen euro over van Borussia Mönchengladbach. Bij de nummer twee van het vorige seizoen, Feyenoord, vindt een leegloop plaats. Hoe vergaat het de nieuwe trainer Fred Rutten in Rotterdam-Zuid? FC Dordrecht keert na twintig jaar weer terug op het hoogste niveau. Lukt het de ploeg van Ernie Brandts om voor de tweede keer in de clubgeschiedenis niet als laatste te eindigen.

programme.title: Thelma og Louise
programme.desc: Somebody said get a life...so they did. In Ridley Scott's adventurous road picture, two friends --unhappy housewife Thelma (Geena Davis) and strong-willed waitress Louise (Susan Sarandon)-- leave responsibilities behind to take a weekend fishing trip in the mountains in their 1966 T-bird convertible. But...at a roadside honky-tonk, where they stop to 'blow off steam,' a man tries to rape Thelma. Louise reacts by shooting the creep with a .38, and this action turns them into dazed and confused fugitives. Now the subject of a nationwide hunt, they regain their determination and recklessness. The film concludes at the Grand Canyon with an indelible image of their final declaration of freedom.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T5 E3 · Red Bull Soapbox Race – Seattle
programme.desc: · Brave teams send their homemade soapbox racers down the steepest course in Red Bull Soapbox history. In front of 40,000 fans, the teams will also have to raise the bar in creativity and showmanship.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T5 E4 · Red Bull Soapbox Race – Turin
programme.desc: · Sixty-one teams of racers throw caution to the wind and send their handmade soapbox racers down a harrowing course filled with jumps, bumps, and berms. It's a crazy, creative and crash-filled day.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T6 E1 · Red Bull Soapbox Race – Holland
programme.desc: · The action in Valkenburg is off to a blistering start as these fearless Dutch drivers zoom down Holland’s steepest road. Gangsters, elephants, and giant pieces of cake race to reach the bottom first.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T6 E2 · Red Bull Soapbox Race – Cincinnati
programme.desc: · Determined soapbox racers unveil their zany creations and face off against Cincinnati’s winding race course.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T6 E3 · Red Bull Soapbox Race – Montreal
programme.desc: · It's chaos in Canada as hairbrained homebrewed racecars blast through a turbulent track in downtown Montreal.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T6 E4 · Red Bull Soapbox Race – London
programme.desc: · Teams of intrepid racers descend the hills near Alexandra Palace in crazy homemade soapbox cars. The obstacle-filled race is a 420m test of engineering, bravery, and (of course) pageantry.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T6 E5 · Red Bull Soapbox Race – Atlanta
programme.desc: · The course in Atlanta, USA, is one of the steepest and fastest to ever be featured in a Red Bull Soapbox Race, putting the durability of every homemade soapbox car to the test.

programme.title: For Reals T1 E9
programme.desc: · Snowboarding – or, rather sandboarding – in the desert. Rally cars on frozen lakes. The wackiness of soapbox racing. Skydiving with a motocross bike. It's all in a day's work for Red Bull athletes.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T6 E7 · Red Bull Soapbox Race – Auckland
programme.desc: · One of the most difficult tracks in Red Bull Soapbox Race history, requiring both durability and manoeuvrability, teams' homemade soapbox cars are put to the test.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T7 E1 · Red Bull Soapbox Race – Cork
programme.desc: · Creative and crazy competitors from the British Isles converge on Cork, Ireland for the Red Bull Soapbox Race.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T7 E2 · Red Bull Soapbox Race – Mumbai
programme.desc: · Thousands of frenzied fans swarm to Mumbai, India, to watch brave soapbox racers compete in the Red Bull Soapbox Race.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T7 E3 · Red Bull Soapbox Race – Chile
programme.desc: · The Andes mountains provide a stunning backdrop to the Red Bull Soapbox Race in Santiago, Chile. Teams of brave racers try to be the fastest through the course filled with obstacles and hairpin turns.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T7 E4 · Best of Red Bull Soapbox Race
programme.desc: · With 20 years of history, there's no shortage of highlights from the Red Bull Soapbox Race. Relive the best moments of this crucible of creativity and craziness right here.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T8 E5 · Best of Red Bull Soapbox Race vol. 2
programme.desc: · Countdown the most memorable moments of Red Bull Soapbox Race, from the impeccable driving skills to the high speed spills take look at weird and wonderful events around the globe.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T8 E1 · Rome, Italy
programme.desc: · The capital city of Italy is a melting pot of fashion, food and history, but Rome is about to show a different side of itself as Red Bull Soapbox Race gets started in this magnificent location.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T8 E2 · Cincinnati, Ohio
programme.desc: · Thousands gather in Cincinnati, Ohio, USA, to witness these wacky contraptions compete downhill against their biggest opponent… gravity.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T8 E3 · Lisbon, Portugal
programme.desc: · The steep inclines of Lisbon, Portugal, played a perfect host to Red Bull Soapbox Race to provide the right amount of thrills as teams soared down in their own soapbox cart creations.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T8 E4 · Red Bull Soapbox Race – Johannesburg
programme.desc: · South Africa's most innovative and witty teams race each other down the twists and turns of Sandton Drive in Johannesburg for Red Bull Soapbox Race.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T9 E1 · Red Bull Soapbox Race 2019 – São Paulo
programme.desc: · The world's craziest and most creative four-wheeled race went to Brazil for intrepid teams to take on the tricky course with their homemade soapbox cars.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T9 E2 · Red Bull Soapbox Race 2019 – Helsinki
programme.desc: · The craziest four-wheeled race headed to Finland as teams and their homemade soapbox cars took on Red Bull Soapbox Race 2019.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T9 E3 · Red Bull Soapbox Race 2019 – Lithuania
programme.desc: · Red Bull Soapbox Race went to Lithuania's second-largest city, Kaunas, where the teams behind the hilarious motorless race cars had the time of their lives.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T9 E4 · Red Bull Soapbox Race 2019 – Dallas
programme.desc: · Red Bull Soapbox Race returned to Dallas, Texas, for intrepid teams to take their homemade soapbox creations and hurtle them down the tricky and hilarious course.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T9 E5 · Red Bull Soapbox Race 2019 – Tokyo
programme.desc: · Creativity reaches new heights at the 2019 Red Bull Soapbox Race in Tokyo, Japan. as the soapbox racers hurtle down a challenging, obstacle-filled course.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race – Iowa T1 E1
programme.desc: · The judges are ready to be dazzled by creativity and fast descents from the racers and their homemade soapbox racers in Iowa, USA.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T10 E2 · Red Bull Soapbox Race 2022 –San Marino
programme.desc: · The hilarious race with no engine and many obstacles. Have the teams done enough to let their homemade soapboxes race to the finish line, or will the course trip them up.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T10 E3 · Red Bull Soapbox Race 2022 – Spa
programme.desc: · Fearless teams race through obstacles in their engineless machines for the Red Bull Soapbox Race 2022 in Spa, Belgium.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T10 E6 · Red Bull Soapbox Race 2022 – Toulouse
programme.desc: · To win or To(ulouse)? That is the question that will be answered today in this gravity-powered race! May the pink city give strength and courage to the many participants.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T10 E5 · Red Bull Soapbox Race 2022 – Madrid
programme.desc: · A churros-powered descent is taking place in the steep road of Madrid! Who will come out on top and who will crash in the haystacks next to the cheering crowd.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T11 E2 · Red Bull Soapbox 2023 – Australia
programme.desc: · High-speed antics at the Red Bull Soapbox Race 2022 in Melbourne, Australia as wildly creative teams test their homemade racers, bringing crashes, laughs, and fierce competition down under.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T11 E1 · Red Bull Soapbox 2023 – Switzerland
programme.desc: · Join the wild ride at the Red Bull Soapbox Race 2023 in Switzerland as teams race homemade, gravity-powered cars through twists and turns, combining creativity, speed and a few crashes.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T12 E2 · Red Bull Soapbox 2024 – India
programme.desc: · The Red Bull Soapbox Race 2024 in Hyderabad, India, unleashed a wave of chaos as teams navigated a unique, obstacle-filled track. Watch as gravity-powered vehicles race, flip and soar.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T11 E4 · Red Bull Soapbox 2023 – Jordan
programme.desc: · The Red Bull Soapbox Race 2023 in Jordan gives creative teams and their handmade cars a wild track amid Amman’s hills, facing twists, turns and crashes in a colourful display of speed and fun.

programme.title: Red Bull Soapbox Race T11 E3 · Red Bull Soapbox 2023 – Norway
programme.desc: · Teams bring their inventive, homemade racers to a wild Red Bull Soapbox Race in Norway, facing steep hills and sharp turns in a thrilling showdown of speed, creativity and spills.
